         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="Wienbibliothek_H.I.N.-198049_vs"/><anchor type="textConst" xml:id="T_L02460-1"/><hi rend="pre-print">A. S.</hi><note type="textConst" corresp="T_L02460-1">ovaler Absenderkleber</note></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Wien, XVIII.</hi></hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb168815" type="place"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Sternwartestr. 71</hi></hi></rs></addrLine></address><address><addrLine>Herrn Felix Braun</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb69" type="place">Wien XIX</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb1092" type="place">Sieveringer Hptstr 149</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="Wienbibliothek_H.I.N.-198049_rs"/><date>26/12 925</date></dateline><salute>lieber Herr Felix Braun,</salute></opener><p>Ihre schönen Worte über die »<rs ref="#pmb30751" type="work">Frau des Richters</rs>«
               haben mich herzlich erfreut. Vielen Dank und die besten Wünsche und Grüße zum neuen
               Jahr.</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur Schnitzler</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
